{"word":"H6452 - פָּסַח - pâçach - paw-sakh' - Halt","slug":"H6452","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">פָּסַח</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>pâçach"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>paw-sakh'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Halt"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E4;&#x05BC;&#x05E1;&#x05D7; - pa&#x0302;sach</b> - <i>paw-sakh'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>hop</i>, that is, (figuratively) <i>skip</i> over (or <i>spare</i>); by implication to <i>hesitate</i>; also (literally) to <i>limp</i>, to <i>dance: - </i>halt, become lame, leap, pass over."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H6454\">H6454</a>, <a href=\"#/H6455\">H6455</a>, <a href=\"#/H6457\">H6457</a>"}]}